des:
Brilliance Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off your smart devices.

There's no need to use remote controller or any app. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off you home appliance, just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo show.

After conecting Alexa to your Brilliance Smart products in a few steps.
1.Download our Brilliance Smart app for Android or iOS;
2.Register on Brilliance Smart app;
3.You need to have some Brilliance Smart devices;
4.Configure your device on Brilliance Smart app and change appropiate name for your devices which will be used in Brilliance Smart Skill;
5.Download Amazon Alexa app for Android or iOS;
6.Search Brilliance Smart skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
7.Click enable skill of "Brilliance Smart" and you'll be navigated to Brilliance Smart login page;
8.Sign in to your Brilliance Smart account with username and password, you'll be redirected to the success page;

Now all setup and finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

* Alexa, turn on light
* Alexa, turn off light
* Alexa, set light brightness to 25%
* Alexa, set light to blue
